♪ BROKEN HEART TO DREAM

277
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:33,463 
♪ 熱い涙を 貴方に上げる

278
00:19:33,589 --> 00:19:38,427 
♪ YOU ARE EVERYTHING TO ME

279
00:19:39,469 --> 00:19:42,389 
♪～

280
